metadata.name: Wanderlust
metadata.description:
Vals, Graubuenden, Switzerland • June 2022 • 
The first shot of the first roll of 35mm film shooting my ‘Alpine Reverie’ series • 2964x1965px, jpg • edition 100/100. 

Airdrop for bidders on my ‘Alpine Reverie’ 1/1 collection on FND.  
Place a bid on any of the 1/1 pieces in ‘Alpine Reverie’  - get 1x Wanderlust. Place two bids - get 2x Wanderlust. Three bids - 3x Wanderlust etc. This piece will serve as utility for future drops.
